name: Ana
factOne: Ana's story draws parallels with the story of Horus from Egyptian mythology. During an altercation with a former friend (in this case, Widowmaker), she lost her cybernetic eye.
factTwo: She continues to experience phantom pain from her eye injury.
factFour: At some point, Fareeha (her daughter Pharah) asked for a toy rifle, but Ana refused, telling her daughter that she'd shoot her eye out. She later came to regret her comments.
factFive: Ana and Jack Morrison (Soldier 76) had a very close friendship fighting side by side to take down Talon and Reaper

name: Ashe
factOne: Ashe's nickname, Calamity, is possibly a reference to famed American frontiers-woman Calamity Jane.
factTwo: B.O.B. will wave back to Ashe if she waves at him in-game.
factThree: Was imprisoned at 17 after stabbing two class mates in self-defense. This is where she met cell mate Jesse Mcree
factFour: She and McCree never dated. According to McCree, Ashe wasn't his type, as per her wealth. McCree knew how to 'push her buttons' better than anyone else.
factFive: After McCree joined Overwatch, Ashe kept a photo of him on her dart board

name: Baptiste
factOne: Jean-Baptiste Augustin is a French name derived from two saints, Saint John the Baptist and Saint Augustine of Hippo.
factTwo: Jean Baptiste was also the name of a french noble during the 18th century who later became the king of Sweden under the name Karl XIV Johan
